{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f98f04b0cb","title":"在袁仲贤关于梅农同申健谈西藏问题报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3b27bf4621","index":0,"year":1950,"month":10,"day":28,"articleId":"f98f04b0cb"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"4cd7ec8bee","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"袁仲贤，当时任中国驻印度大使。"},{"id":"ec5d5705d8","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"梅农，当时任印度外交部次长。"},{"id":"bc0af71d36","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"申健，当时任中国驻印度大使馆政务参赞。14]1950年10月26日梅农约请中健谈西藏问题，说中国军队进入西藏的消息如为事实，印度政府深感遗撼，并向申健提交了印度政府关于西藏问题致中国政府照会的副本。申健指出，在印度报纸上时常着到的中国“侵略”西藏的字样，在印度政府照会上也使用了，这样的用法是不对的。中国军队进入中国的领土西藏是不能叫侵略的，正如印度政府的军队进入印度联合省或孟买不能叫侵略一样。梅农说，印度仍望中国用和平方式解决西藏问题。申健说，中国政府始终愿用和平方式解决西藏问题，但这并不等于说中国军队不能进入西藏。"}],"contents":[{"id":"4bec5baacb","type":"title","text":"在袁仲贤“关于梅农同申健谈西藏问题报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb"},{"id":"4cd7ec8bee","type":"paragraph","text":"周，并外交部：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb"},{"id":"ec5d5705d8","type":"paragraph","text":"申健答得很正确，态度还应强硬一点，应说中国军队是必须到达西藏一切应到的地方，无论西藏地方政府愿意谈判与否及谈判结果如何，任何外国对此无置哆的余地","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb"},{"id":"bc0af71d36","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb"},{"id":"9dda545c0a","type":"paragraph","text":"十月廿八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb"}],"page":{"id":"bab09f043f","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"f98f04b0cb","start":315,"end":315}}}},"__N_SSG":true}